OL,6,FMore than 70,000 staff at 150
OL,7,Funiversities across the UK will strike
OL,8,Ffor 18 days between February and March
OL,9,Fin disputes over pay, conditions and
OL,10,Fpensions.
OL,12,FThe action, called by the University
OL,13,Fand College Union (UCU), will be the
OL,14,Flatest in a long list of strikes that
OL,15,Fhave affected everything from rail
OL,16,Fservices and Royal Mail deliveries to
OL,17,FBorder Force operations in recent
OL,18,Fmonths, and will follow nurses and
OL,19,Femergency service workers walking out
OL,20,Fthis month in the biggest strike in the
OL,21,Fhistory of the NHS.
